WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.964
Among these towering industry giants, Amazon Web Services stands entirely

00:00:03.964 --> 00:00:07.928
apart as the true, undisputed global market leader. They lead

00:00:07.928 --> 00:00:11.892
the industry not only in pure infrastructure market share and

00:00:11.892 --> 00:00:15.856
direct revenue, but critically, in the maturity, sheer scale, and

00:00:15.856 --> 00:00:19.820
strategic prioritization of their partner collaborations across the globe.
